*---------------------------------------+--------------------------------+-------------------------+------------------+
 net.sf.ghost4j.renderer.SimpleRenderer | Render a range of pages from a  |Yes					   |Yes
 									    | document to images. 			 |						   |
*---------------------------------------+--------------------------------+-------------------------+------------------+

